t season, have also recently signed Arsenal goalkeeper Emiliano Martinez and Nottingham Forest right-back Matty Cash. Smith’s side kick off their Premier League campaign at home to Sheffield United on Monday. [AFP] Vanguard News Nigeria. "He's physically a man, and he has been for some time. He's a big powerful boy, very quick, dynamic and a maverick-type player. Those players are few and far between. August 14, 2015 In "News" Chelsea forward Bertrand Traore has joined Lyon for 10 million euros (£8.8m, $11.2m) on a five-year deal, the French club announced on Monday. June 26, 2017 In "Sports" Brazilian striker Wesley scored twice and missed a penalty as Aston Villa thumped injury-hit Norwich City 5-1 at Carrow Road for their biggest Premier League away win in 11 years. Jack Grealish, Conor Hourihane and Douglas Luiz completed the rout for Aston Villa, with Josip Drmic scoring a late consolation… October 6, 2019 In "Sports"